OL,3,CRecord number of Guernsey islanders
OL,4,Ctake part in clothes swap event
OL,6,FMichael Maitland-Jones reports:
OL,8,FThe number of islanders taking part in
OL,9,FThe Clean Earth Trust's most recent
OL,10,Fclothes swap has doubled in a year.
OL,12,FOn Saturday (3 February) a total of 96
OL,13,Fpeople brought 525 items of clothing
OL,14,Fto the event, and 417 pieces were
OL,15,Ftaken away.
OL,17,FIn comparison, 46 islanders attended
OL,18,Fthe event last February bringing 272
OL,19,Fitems.
