OL,3,CRecord number of Guernsey islanders
OL,4,Ctake part in clothes swap event
OL,6,FOrganiser Emily Gabb says people were
OL,7,Fqueuing out of the door at the KGV
OL,8,FCommunity Centre ready to swap items.
OL,10,FShe adds: "It's really growing, I mean
OL,11,Fweek by week we're seeing the numbers
OL,12,Fgo up. The amount of clothing we see
OL,13,Fcome in is incredible and actually the
OL,14,Famount of clothing which goes out
OL,15,Fnearly matches that."
OL,17,FThe idea behind the clothes swap is
OL,18,Fsimple. Each person arrives with 10
OL,19,Fitems, you then browse the rails and
OL,20,Ftables and leave with up to the same
OL,21,Famount of different items.
