OL,4,Ctake part in clothes swap event
OL,6,FEmily says that due to its growing
OL,7,Fpopularity, the trust has already had
OL,8,Fto move the swap to a bigger location.
OL,10,F"We didn't expect it to get this
OL,11,Fpopular. We're possibly outgrowing
OL,12,Fwhere we are now, but you know, we
OL,13,Fonly have so many volunteers that help
OL,14,Fbecause we are run on a volunteer
OL,15,Fbasis."
OL,17,FWhile helping islanders to save money
OL,18,Fthe trust also hopes the scheme will
OL,19,Fcut down on garments ending up in the
OL,20,Frubbish.
