OL,3,CRecord number of Guernsey islanders
OL,4,Ctake part in clothes swap event
OL,6,FOne islander taking part told ITV
OL,7,FNews: "I think it's just fun. It's
OL,8,Flike going shopping but actually not
OL,9,Fspending money.
OL,11,F"The way that the cost of living is,
OL,12,Fit's just insane. I'd rather go out
OL,13,Ffor a few nice meals than go and buy
OL,14,Fsome expensive clothes."
OL,16,FAnother said: "I can bring things here
OL,17,Fand then come away with some new
OL,18,Fthings. I love it so much. It's such a
OL,19,Fgood thing to do."
