OL,4,Ctake part in clothes swap event
OL,6,FIn addition to the clothes swap, a
OL,7,Frepair cafe also took place with more
OL,8,Fthan 20 electrical, DIY and textile
OL,9,Ffixes completed.
OL,11,FThe Clean Earth Trust's next venture
OL,12,Fis to introduce a clothes swap in
OL,13,Fschools dedicated to childrenswear.
OL,15,FThe next swap for adult clothing takes
OL,16,Fplace on 16 March at St Martins
OL,17,FCommunity Centre.
